00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:31.820
(Lu Zhuo)

00:01:32.060 --> 00:01:35.380
(Lady Yuan of the Su family, Su Jinyuan)

00:01:35.900 --> 00:01:36.900
Lady Yuan.

00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:39.500
You abandoned the Xiao family
to run away with me.

00:01:40.220 --> 00:01:42.060
In this life, I, Lu Zhuo,

00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:43.700
will never fail you.

00:02:19.900 --> 00:02:20.940
Lu Zhuo.

00:02:23.140 --> 00:02:25.020
This moment

00:02:26.260 --> 00:02:28.180
is exactly as it was

00:02:29.980 --> 00:02:31.539
in our past life.

00:02:31.540 --> 00:02:33.140
What?

00:02:47.780 --> 00:02:50.540
In our past life, you taught me
how to read the human heart.

00:02:51.180 --> 00:02:52.620
In this life,

00:02:52.820 --> 00:02:55.260
I will send you to hell!

00:03:17.060 --> 00:03:19.939
Run! The Xiao family's adopted son
Xie Yunyan has rebelled!

00:03:19.940 --> 00:03:22.740
They are about to
break into the imperial city!

00:03:24.580 --> 00:03:25.940
Run!

00:03:26.060 --> 00:03:26.819
Go!

00:03:26.820 --> 00:03:28.060
Move!

00:03:28.060 --> 00:03:29.459
Still thinking about the Xiao family?

00:03:29.460 --> 00:03:30.800
They colluded with the enemy
and betrayed the realm!

00:03:30.800 --> 00:03:32.180
They were wiped out. Understand?

00:03:32.900 --> 00:03:34.020
Go!

00:03:35.140 --> 00:03:35.940
Go!

00:03:36.620 --> 00:03:37.500
Are you going or not?

00:03:37.660 --> 00:03:38.459
Are you going or not?

00:03:38.460 --> 00:03:39.580
It is useless.

00:03:42.020 --> 00:03:43.540
You still cannot bear to leave?

00:03:44.100 --> 00:03:45.620
Still reluctant to go?

00:04:08.060 --> 00:04:11.380
(The Xiao family's adopted son,
Xie Yunyan)

00:04:59.060 --> 00:05:01.260
Lady Yuan of the Su family.

00:05:02.260 --> 00:05:03.660
Xie Yunyan.

00:05:07.220 --> 00:05:09.900
Back then, you ran away
with this adulterer.

00:05:10.100 --> 00:05:12.020
My elder brother lost all honor.

00:05:12.300 --> 00:05:14.380
You made the Xiao family
a laughingstock.

00:05:15.860 --> 00:05:16.899
I ask you to judge fairly.

00:05:16.900 --> 00:05:17.580
I...

00:05:17.820 --> 00:05:19.059
I ask you to judge fairly.

00:05:19.060 --> 00:05:19.660
I...

00:05:19.740 --> 00:05:20.220
I...

00:05:20.260 --> 00:05:22.940
I was tempted by this faithless woman.

00:05:26.500 --> 00:05:27.460
Lu Zhuo.

00:05:28.140 --> 00:05:30.500
You clearly vowed
we would stay true to each other.

00:05:30.780 --> 00:05:32.300
That was why I...

00:05:32.340 --> 00:05:33.220
Shut up!

00:05:37.300 --> 00:05:39.340
Those who betray the Xiao family

00:05:40.220 --> 00:05:41.980
must die.

00:06:18.620 --> 00:06:19.540
Sir.

00:06:19.740 --> 00:06:20.739
Sir, look.

00:06:20.740 --> 00:06:22.619
I have already killed this wretch.

00:06:22.620 --> 00:06:24.140
Will you not spare me?

00:06:29.620 --> 00:06:30.619
To think you would

00:06:30.620 --> 00:06:33.540
betray the Xiao family
for such a faithless creature.

00:06:37.940 --> 00:06:39.220
Enough.

00:06:40.780 --> 00:06:42.740
Go to the underworld

00:06:44.020 --> 00:06:46.580
and answer for
what you owe the Xiao family.

00:06:47.420 --> 00:06:49.619
Slaughter every
treacherous court official

00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:51.700
in honor of the
Xiao family's fallen heroes.

00:06:51.740 --> 00:06:53.940
Slaughter every
treacherous court official

00:06:54.020 --> 00:06:56.420
in honor of the
Xiao family's fallen heroes.

00:07:11.260 --> 00:07:11.860
You...

00:07:11.980 --> 00:07:13.020
You are mad.

00:07:14.340 --> 00:07:16.100
You used news of my brother

00:07:16.460 --> 00:07:18.140
to trick me into fleeing the marriage.

00:07:19.140 --> 00:07:21.620
You used the name of a first wife

00:07:21.820 --> 00:07:24.460
to make me give you my whole heart.

00:07:24.980 --> 00:07:26.140
You deceived me,

00:07:26.180 --> 00:07:27.540
humiliated me,

00:07:27.620 --> 00:07:29.260
trampled on me,

00:07:29.500 --> 00:07:31.780
and you even want to kill me.

00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:39.900
The one who truly deserves death

00:07:41.180 --> 00:07:42.660
is you!

00:08:26.900 --> 00:08:28.580
(What belonged to the past life)

00:08:29.380 --> 00:08:31.020
(has turned to dust.)

00:08:33.740 --> 00:08:34.980
(In this life,)

00:08:36.300 --> 00:08:39.220
(I will become
a completely new Su Jinyuan.)

00:10:22.980 --> 00:10:24.219
Is anyone there?

00:10:24.220 --> 00:10:25.460
Please help me.

00:10:33.180 --> 00:10:34.700
(Xie Yunyan?)

00:10:35.180 --> 00:10:37.100
Those who betray the Xiao family

00:10:37.140 --> 00:10:38.500
must die.

00:10:43.140 --> 00:10:45.100
Lady Yuan of the Su family.

00:10:46.980 --> 00:10:48.420
The fire at the ancient temple

00:10:49.060 --> 00:10:50.780
was your doing.

00:10:57.740 --> 00:10:59.420
I know you intend to kill me.

00:11:00.140 --> 00:11:01.380
Save your strength.

00:11:23.860 --> 00:11:26.740
You would throw your life away
just to escape this marriage.

00:11:29.460 --> 00:11:30.740
I did not escape.

00:11:32.900 --> 00:11:34.180
Lu Zhuo deceived me.

00:11:34.580 --> 00:11:36.540
He told me there was
news of my missing brother.

00:11:37.060 --> 00:11:38.660
That was why I left the city with him.

00:11:45.660 --> 00:11:47.180
In the end,

00:11:47.260 --> 00:11:48.940
I was the one
who wronged the Xiao family.

00:11:53.300 --> 00:11:54.899
Shall I then help you, Young Lady Su,

00:11:54.900 --> 00:11:56.380
drag Lu Zhuo here,

00:11:56.700 --> 00:11:57.899
skin him,

00:11:57.900 --> 00:11:59.500
grind his bones,

00:11:59.620 --> 00:12:01.300
and make him atone to you?

00:12:05.140 --> 00:12:06.740
That is my own matter.

00:12:07.380 --> 00:12:08.539
It does not concern you.

00:12:08.540 --> 00:12:10.219
Even now

00:12:10.220 --> 00:12:11.859
you still defend that adulterer?

00:12:11.860 --> 00:12:13.340
I am not.

00:12:14.020 --> 00:12:15.460
Come back to the Xiao family with me.

00:12:15.700 --> 00:12:17.100
Before the ancestral hall,

00:12:17.180 --> 00:12:18.620
you will explain everything yourself.

00:12:19.740 --> 00:12:21.780
(Three months after the wedding
in the past life,)

00:12:21.900 --> 00:12:23.860
(the Xiao father and son
were defeated at Linchuan,)

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:26.200
