00:14:25.580 --> 00:14:27.819
Xiao family holds the title
of Duke who guards the realm.

00:14:27.820 --> 00:14:29.699
My elder brother is gentle and valiant.

00:14:29.700 --> 00:14:30.680
Yet you fled the marriage

00:14:30.680 --> 00:14:32.580
